name: Roots
description:
Ganimation_still is a ganimation facets.

This project is growing with many angles as my condition.
Feeling burned out and emotionally drained is a long rehabilitation process.
Ganimation project was created as a therapeutic form of treatment to take my mind off the burnout I am currently living. Using vqgan-clip  with the text prompt from what I see through my window looking at the forest I have the chance to live in.
Then, i manually edit the AI outpout. 
This project is meant to give me the opportunity to get back to my roots as a permaculturist and an artist.
